ent-RMCJumpsuitCivilianFrontier-name = frontier jumpsuit
ent-RMCJumpsuitCivilianFrontier-desc = A cargo jumpsuit dressed down for full range of motion and state-of-the-art frontier temperature control. It's the best thing an engineer can wear in the Outer Veil.

ent-RMCJumpsuitCLFSoldier-name = Colonial Liberation Front uniform
ent-RMCJumpsuitCLFSoldier-desc = A stylish grey-green jumpsuit - standard issue for colonists. This version appears to have the symbol of the Colonial Liberation Front emblazoned in select areas.

ent-RMCJumpsuitCivilianEngineerWorker-name = Weston-Yamada engineering utility uniform
ent-RMCJumpsuitCivilianEngineerWorker-desc = A set of Weston-Yamada engineering utility workers uniform, a orange pair of work slacks and a grey polo-shirt with orange reflecting stripes.

ent-RMCJumpsuitCivilianJanitor-name = janitor's jumpsuit
ent-RMCJumpsuitCivilianJanitor-desc = It's the official uniform of the colony's janitor.

ent-RMCJumpsuitUNSecurity-name = Униформа службы безопасности Организации Объединенных Наций

ent-RMCJumpsuitCivilianSecurity-name = security officer's jumpsuit
ent-RMCJumpsuitCivilianSecurity-desc = It's made of a slightly sturdier material than standard jumpsuits, to allow for robust protection.

ent-RMCJumpsuitKutjevoDrysuit-name = kutjevo drysuit
ent-RMCJumpsuitKutjevoDrysuit-desc = A heavy-duty drysuit worn by the workers on Kutjevo.

ent-RMCJumpsuitKutjevoJumper-name = kutjevo jumper
ent-RMCJumpsuitKutjevoJumper-desc = A heavy-duty jumpsuit worn by the workers on Kutjevo.

ent-RMCJumpsuitLaborersOveralls-name = laborer's overalls
ent-RMCJumpsuitLaborersOveralls-desc = A set of durable overalls for getting the job done.

ent-RMCJumpsuitEMT-name = EMT - Paramedic uniform
ent-RMCJumpsuitEMT-desc = A set of EMT - Paramedic fatigues, this one is red.

ent-RMCJumpsuitDoctor-name = medical doctor's uniform
ent-RMCJumpsuitDoctor-desc = They're made of a special fiber that provides minor protection against biohazards. They have a cross on the chest denoting that the wearer is trained medical personnel.

ent-RMCJumpsuitTMCC-name = tartarus-mining uniform
ent-RMCJumpsuitTMCC-desc = A set of Tartarus-Mining fatigues, a yellow pair of utility work slacks and a light-grey polo-shirt with red reflecting stripes.

ent-RMCJumpsuitDailyGrind-name = The Daily Grind uniform
ent-RMCJumpsuitDailyGrind-desc = A pair of black slacks and a white short-sleeved button-down shirt; a standard uniform for a 'The Daily Grind' employee. Are you ready for the daily grind?

ent-RMCJumpsuitPizzaGalaxy-name = Pizza-Galaxy uniform
ent-RMCJumpsuitPizzaGalaxy-desc = A pair of red slacks and a white button-down shirt with a large 'Pizza-Galaxy' logo on the back; a standard uniform for a Pizza-Galaxy employee. Pizza-Galaxy! To infinity and beyond!

ent-RMCJumpsuitSanitation-name = Weston-Yamada RFF - sanitation uniform
ent-RMCJumpsuitSanitation-desc = A set of Weston-Yamada RFF - Sanitation fatigues, a green pair of work slacks and a grey polo-shirt with green reflecting stripes.

ent-RMCJumpsuitWeyamart-name = Weyamart uniform
ent-RMCJumpsuitWeyamart-desc = A pair of dark-grey slacks and an orange button-down shirt; a standard uniform for the Weston-Yamada branded supermarket 'Weyamart'.

ent-RMCJumpsuitSteward-name = steward utilities
ent-RMCJumpsuitSteward-desc = A stylish brown vest and shorts - uniforms like this are often worn by clerks and shop stewards.

ent-RMCJumpsuitOrange-name = orange jumpsuit
ent-RMCJumpsuitOrange-desc = It's standardised prisoner-wear. Its suit sensors are stuck in the "Fully On" position.

ent-RMCJumpsuitCivilianScientist-name = scientist's utility jumpsuit
ent-RMCJumpsuitCivilianScientist-desc = It's made of a special fiber that provides minor protection against biohazards. It has markings that denote the wearer as a scientist.

ent-RMCJumpsuitCivilianVirologist-name = virologist's uniform
ent-RMCJumpsuitCivilianVirologist-desc = It's made of a special fiber that gives special protection against biohazards. It has a virologist rank stripe on it.

ent-RMCJumpsuitChaplain-name = chaplain's jumpsuit
ent-RMCJumpsuitChaplain-desc = It's a black jumpsuit, often worn by religious folk.

ent-RMCJumpsuitRedShorts-name = red shorts
ent-RMCJumpsuitRedShorts-desc = A ratty pair of red shorts. Smells of cigarettes.

